changed to:

ChangeEffect

Problems with Symbols, Medium Severity (23)

SDL_error.h, libSDL-1.2.so.0.11.4
[+] SDL_GetError ( ) (1)
ChangeEffect
1Type of return value became const (has been changed from char* to char const*).The return value will be treated as non-const by old client applications. This may result in crash or incorrect behavior of applications.


SDL_events.h, libSDL-1.2.so.0.11.4
[+] SDL_GetEventFilter ( ) (3)
changed to:
SDL_GetEventFilter ( int(*filter)(void*, SDL_Event*)*, void** userdata )
ChangeEffect
1The pointer level of return value has been decreased from 1 to 0.Applications may try to access unallocated memory by the dereferencing of new return value and therefore cause a crash.
2Parameter filter of type SDL_EventFilter* has been added to the calling stack.This parameter will not be initialized by old clients.
3Parameter userdata of type void** has been added to the calling stack.This parameter will not be initialized by old clients.
